title: MSRLM Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for 05 IFC Block Anchor Posts
description: The Maharashtra State Rural Livelihoods Mission (MSRLM) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 05 IFC Block Anchor Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their B.E./B. Tech, B.Sc., can apply for the MSRLM Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can apply in offline mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process...
